Time for a short fast post.  Lately life has been ok...........I mean i can't really complain.  I'm going to college, i own a car, i have a decent life.  I've just been unhappy lately.  And so fucking lost it's ridiculous.  Like i just don't know where i'm going to be in 1 year, what school i'll be going to, what major i'll have, where i'll be living.  That kinda scares me.  I don't know i just feel lost.  And on the topic of women well............Most girls don't interest me at all.  I don't know why.  Seriously i just can't find anyone interesting enough to be attracted to.  For me personality is key and looks are secondary, although certain looks usually define certain personalities.  I can't handle "normal" girls because they don't challenge me, I like when girls fight playfully and argue with me.  My last date, a lunch date with a girl from my french class, was boring as fuck, mostly because we had nothing incommon, i sorta asked her out cause she was cute.......well that didn't work out cause i liked nothing about her except that she was cute, go figure.  But yeah eventually i'll find a girl who just knocks me off my feet, one who is crazy/amazing/interesting/beautiful.  I'm genuinely looking forward to that day.......if that day will ever come.  I think girls are another reason i feel lost.  Don't get me wrong i have the most amazing female friends but........but whatever yeah that's right.  I shouldn't be fucking complaining so many people have it so much harder.  I just want to be happy instead of just going through life.  Not to mention right now i'm sooooooo fucking lonely.  My two closest friends are away at their respective schools and i'm going to my school.  And they are brilliant so they get so much homework i never really get to talk to them.  My other really great friend is in highschool and he's really busy with their musical.  and my OTHER good friend he's spread thinly at his school and having many of his own problems.  Guess this entry wasn't as short as i thought it was going to be.  I wonder how many people are actually going to read this.  Sure i jumped around a lot but hey it happens, and although i talked about girls mooooooooooooost, my friends and school and life bother me way more than that, it's just girls are easier to complain about haha.  I'm a bastard.
